de.mpa.client.model.dbsearch

Class ProteinHit

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mpa.client.model.dbsearch.ProteinHit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Taxonomic, Hit, Serializable, Comparable<ProteinHit>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MascotStorager.MascotProteinHit, MetaProteinHit

    public class ProteinHit
extends Object
implements Serializable, Comparable<ProteinHit>, Taxonomic, Hit
    This class represents an identified protein hit. It contains information about accession, description and a list of associated peptide hits.
    Author:
    T. Muth, R. Heyer, A. Behne, F. Kohrs
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
